name: Hubble Protocol
reason: A borrowing protocol enabling the minting of USDH against collateral. Generates protocol revenue through minting and redemption fees. Moderate governance concentration.

name: SonarWatch
reason: The premier portfolio tracking dashboard for Solana. Essential infrastructure for users to track DeFi positions. Token allows for PRO features and governance.

name: Frakt
reason: A decentralized NFT lending protocol. Allows users to borrow against NFTs or lend liquidity for yield. Generates real revenue from interest spreads.

name: MonkeyLeague
reason: A strategy-based soccer game. High production value but relies on the play-to-earn model which carries economic sustainability risks. Moderate to high insider influence.

name: Investin
reason: A decentralized fund management protocol allowing traders to launch on-chain funds. Provides systemic utility for copy-trading, though liquidity is niche.

name: ALL.ART
reason: Infrastructure focusing on NFT licensing and rights management standards (VRDA). Builds critical intellectual property rails for the ecosystem.

name: Crowny
reason: Advertising platform connecting brands with users via a loyalty app. Token value is tied to brand adoption and ad-spend within the closed ecosystem.

name: Liq Protocol
reason: A decentralized liquidation engine powering other lending protocols. Critical backend infrastructure, but high insider score due to the technical niche and team control.

name: SolRazr
reason: One of the original IDO launchpads on Solana. Token acts as a gatekeeper for allocations. Value fluctuates heavily based on the quality of launched projects.

name: Cyclos
reason: Concentrated liquidity market maker. While technologically sound, it struggles for market share against dominant aggregators, increasing the speculative risk for holders.
